33:32.510 --> 33:34.887
- You gonna do something here?
- I'm doing it, farm boy.

33:34.971 --> 33:37.282
Not that you deserve it.
You're a witch hunter, aren't you?

33:37.307 --> 33:38.349
She still loves you.

33:39.267 --> 33:41.810
<i>Qui affecto protego,
mixtisque iubas serpentibus</i>

33:41.894 --> 33:43.730
<i>et posteris meis stirpiqu.</i>

33:46.816 --> 33:47.858
Susie...

33:48.943 --> 33:49.943
did you see that?

34:05.835 --> 34:07.211
My name is Susie Putnam.

34:09.380 --> 34:11.675
Blood of Dorothea Putnam,

34:11.757 --> 34:14.260
who gave you passage across
the ocean when no one else would,

34:14.344 --> 34:17.639
who cut you down from the hanging tree
when no one else would.

34:18.222 --> 34:19.849
The Walkers are my friends.

34:22.601 --> 34:23.893
Please don't hurt them.

34:35.197 --> 34:38.242
It's working, isn't it?
The protection spell, Aunt Zelda?

34:38.326 --> 34:41.246
Yes, as long as we four
remain focused, it just might.

34:46.041 --> 34:48.210
Faustus, you brought me here?

34:48.295 --> 34:50.855
- I did, Sister Zelda...
- I have to go back. My family needs me.

34:50.922 --> 34:52.922
Your sworn duty is here, Zelda!

34:53.007 --> 34:54.884
Lady Blackwood has gone into labor.

34:58.597 --> 34:59.847
Damn you, Faustus.

35:00.639 --> 35:03.351
I'll need clean towels, fresh water,
and Prudence.

35:03.434 --> 35:06.313
- Prudence?
- Yes, I'll need help,

35:06.396 --> 35:08.188
and this is no place for a man.

35:08.648 --> 35:10.733
And that very much includes you.

35:15.030 --> 35:16.030
Yes.

35:17.364 --> 35:18.824
You'll be just fine.

35:21.911 --> 35:23.621
Where did Aunt Zelda go?
What is happening?

35:23.704 --> 35:25.873
Can the protection spell hold
with just three of us?

35:25.956 --> 35:30.128
It's a bit dodgy, but if three of us just
pick up the slack and no one else disap...

35:30.628 --> 35:31.628
No!

35:33.547 --> 35:34.840
Luke, what am I doing here?

35:34.923 --> 35:37.217
I teleported you here.
It's no use trying to leave.

35:37.302 --> 35:39.342
I've bound you to the Academy,
and you have to stay.

35:39.387 --> 35:42.067
- Why? Why would you do this?
- Because you belong here with us now,

35:42.097 --> 35:44.141
with your own kind,
safe inside these walls,

35:44.224 --> 35:46.268
standing with the coven
with your warlock brothers.

35:46.353 --> 35:47.228
With me, Ambrose.

35:47.311 --> 35:50.565
- No. You don't understand. I have to...
- No, <i>you </i> don't understand!

35:50.648 --> 35:53.025
I couldn't leave you out there
to die, Ambrose.

35:53.525 --> 35:54.985
Because I love you.

36:04.411 --> 36:06.914
The witches are getting stronger
out there, I can sense it.

36:06.998 --> 36:09.458
Ms. Wardwell,
it's just me and Aunt Hilda now.

36:09.833 --> 36:12.253
I'm fading, love.
I don't think I can hold out much longer.

36:12.336 --> 36:15.547
Sabrina, if youÂ and your Aunt
can't maintain the spell,

36:15.632 --> 36:18.300
the Thirteen will throw open
every door and window.

36:18.385 --> 36:21.554
The mortals will be unprotected
when the Red Angel arrives,

36:21.637 --> 36:23.514
and there will be no escaping his sword.

36:23.597 --> 36:24.766
Pitch in at any time.

36:24.849 --> 36:27.811
I fear we would still falter
before the witching hour ends.

36:27.893 --> 36:32.148
Then there's the matter of Mr. Kinkle,
Miss Putnam, Miss Walker.

36:32.231 --> 36:35.943
They're out there,
facing their own personal assaults.

36:36.027 --> 36:38.655
No, the time for defense is over.

36:39.030 --> 36:40.907
It's time to go on the offensive.

36:40.989 --> 36:42.534
How would we even do that?

36:42.617 --> 36:46.079
As a matter of fact, I have an idea,
but it would mean your Aunt Hilda here

36:46.161 --> 36:47.914
holding down the fort alone for a bit.

36:47.996 --> 36:50.583
- Alone? Bloody hell!
- Sabrina, we are running out of time.

36:50.666 --> 36:54.963
Fine, let's do it. Aunt Hilda, hold on.
Salem, stay here and watch Aunt Hilda.

36:56.047 --> 36:58.632
Just do it, Salem!
I'll be back as soon as I can.

37:04.556 --> 37:07.307
<i>In the end,
there was only one way to accomplish</i>

37:07.391 --> 37:09.728
<i>what the Dark Lord wanted.</i>

37:10.561 --> 37:13.398
Make it so that Sabrina would have
no other option.

37:14.940 --> 37:19.027
There would only be one path
to save the mortals.

37:22.197 --> 37:24.451
The Path of Night.

37:25.994 --> 37:28.871
<i>And so we went
back to the clearing in the woods,</i>

37:29.706 --> 37:34.251
<i>where this story first began
16 years ago.</i>

37:34.543 --> 37:35.753
Wait...

37:35.836 --> 37:38.547
Ms. Wardwell,
this is where my Dark Baptism...

37:38.630 --> 37:40.800
...almost but not quite took place.

37:43.677 --> 37:44.721
Ms. Wardwell...

37:45.429 --> 37:47.724
what is the <i>Book of the Beast </i> doing here?

37:49.559 --> 37:50.684
The kind of...

37:51.561 --> 37:54.188
power you'll need
to save Greendale will...

37:54.938 --> 37:56.023
require you to...

37:56.106 --> 37:57.525
Sign my name?

37:58.777 --> 38:01.570
Exchange my freedom for power?

38:03.447 --> 38:06.701
I already said no to this, Ms. Wardwell.

38:06.784 --> 38:09.913
This is what your father
and mother wanted for you.

38:10.496 --> 38:13.041
That wasn't a lie your aunties told you.

38:13.333 --> 38:16.085
The circumstances, you must agree,
have changed.

38:16.878 --> 38:18.630
You're not the same girl,

38:18.713 --> 38:21.673
not the same witch you were
the night of the...

38:22.550 --> 38:24.302
ill-fated baptism.

38:24.802 --> 38:26.346
You have the potential

38:26.846 --> 38:29.807
to be the greatest witch
of your generation.

38:31.726 --> 38:33.894
There is a cost that comes with that.

38:33.978 --> 38:36.438
There has to be another way.

38:37.148 --> 38:38.817
There's not one I can think of.

38:40.818 --> 38:42.152
You must sign.

38:42.445 --> 38:45.572
It's the only way you'll ever
be strong enough to stop...

38:51.746 --> 38:53.039
That's him now.

38:54.916 --> 38:56.668
The Red Angel of Death.

38:57.668 --> 38:58.710
Can you hear him?

39:19.690 --> 39:21.233
I know you're scared, Sabrina.

39:21.733 --> 39:24.945
Because all women are taught
to fear power.

39:26.655 --> 39:28.657
Own your power.

39:29.409 --> 39:31.411
Don't accept it from the Dark Lord.

39:31.494 --> 39:33.371
Take it. Wield it.

39:34.289 --> 39:35.664
Save your friends.

39:35.748 --> 39:37.000
Ms. Wardwell...

39:37.333 --> 39:39.376
You've all but signed already.

39:39.460 --> 39:40.460
But...

39:41.461 --> 39:42.838
What's more important?

39:43.338 --> 39:48.635
That pissing contest with the Dark Lord,
or the salvation of your friends?

39:49.469 --> 39:51.931
If I sign...

39:52.639 --> 39:54.391
It is your destiny.

39:56.059 --> 39:59.271
If you do not, Harvey will die.

40:00.440 --> 40:02.525
Rosalind and Susie will die.

40:03.025 --> 40:05.945
Your aunts and your cousin will die.

40:06.028 --> 40:07.237
I will die.

40:07.697 --> 40:09.364
Please, Sabrina...

40:11.242 --> 40:12.911
for all our sakes.

40:18.916 --> 40:19.916
I'll sign.

40:31.554 --> 40:36.016
Do you do this of your own free will?

40:37.518 --> 40:42.606
And do you understand what it means?

40:44.317 --> 40:49.697
When I call on you, girl, you must answer.

41:15.306 --> 41:18.226
<i>I shall deliver Sabrina unto you.</i>

41:18.309 --> 41:19.726
<i>Mom? Dad?</i>

41:19.811 --> 41:23.188
<i>Oh, my child, you have
no idea how special you are, do you?</i>

41:25.148 --> 41:27.068
<i>There's no flying in my life...</i>

41:28.360 --> 41:29.360
<i>without you.</i>

41:34.242 --> 41:36.452
<i>You must sign the </i> Book of the Beast!

41:36.536 --> 41:37.577
<i>I can't do this.</i>

41:37.661 --> 41:40.998
<i>Sabrina Spellman
shall retain her mortal life,</i>

41:41.081 --> 41:45.753
<i>on the condition that she also attend
the Academy of Unseen Arts.</i>

41:49.507 --> 41:52.010
<i>- Are you ready to meet your fate?
- Prudence, please.</i>

41:52.092 --> 41:54.594
<i>I'm begging you, leave me alone.</i>

41:54.679 --> 41:57.014
<i>There's not a hope
in hell of that, half-breed.</i>

41:57.472 --> 42:00.684
<i>How am I ever going to outwit
the Dark Lord?</i>

42:00.768 --> 42:03.271
<i>Your parents died because of you.</i>

42:07.733 --> 42:09.568
<i>How's that feel?</i>

42:10.402 --> 42:12.155
<i>Not to have faith in anything?</i>

42:15.365 --> 42:16.367
<i>Mom, it's me.</i>

42:16.992 --> 42:19.786
<i>They took my baby after the baptism.</i>

42:19.871 --> 42:22.081
<i>They told me she had died.</i>

42:23.248 --> 42:25.376
<i>It's better to forget the mortal world.</i>

42:26.168 --> 42:28.963
<i>Harvey, please. Let me stay.
Let me at least help...</i>

42:29.088 --> 42:30.297
<i>No, Sabrina. You've...</i>

42:30.380 --> 42:31.507
You've done enough.

42:34.510 --> 42:35.510
You have to go.

42:35.969 --> 42:39.389
<i>Everything has a price.</i>

42:40.516 --> 42:42.726
<i>Edward learned that lesson.</i>

42:43.186 --> 42:44.436
<i>It's your turn now.</i>

42:54.237 --> 42:56.740
Sabrina. Breathe. Let it in.

42:57.784 --> 43:00.494
- Can you feel it? Do you feel it.
- Yes.

43:01.788 --> 43:03.998
- We don't have much time.
- Where...

43:05.123 --> 43:06.125
Where do we go now?

43:07.460 --> 43:09.336
What do we do to stop the Thirteen...

43:09.795 --> 43:10.795
and the Red Angel?

43:12.507 --> 43:14.634
Not we, you.

43:15.550 --> 43:18.721
The power is yours, not ours.

43:19.222 --> 43:20.222
Where do I go?

43:21.891 --> 43:24.351
- What do I do?
- Don't you know, Sabrina?

43:25.936 --> 43:29.481
Hasn't the Dark Lord already shown you
what to do?

43:29.565 --> 43:30.565
What are you...?

43:31.483 --> 43:32.483
I don't...

43:43.121 --> 43:44.789
I was at the Hanging Tree.

43:49.335 --> 43:50.878
Where the witches died.

43:55.590 --> 43:57.260
It was on fire.

44:03.056 --> 44:06.476
We're nearly there, Lady Blackwood.
One more push.

44:07.644 --> 44:10.313
And here comes your first...

44:14.277 --> 44:15.570
What is it?

44:15.652 --> 44:18.447
Nothing. You're doing fine,
Lady Blackwood.

44:18.530 --> 44:20.574
Just think ofÂ how proud
the High Priest will be.

44:20.657 --> 44:22.201
Is he all right, my son?

44:22.284 --> 44:24.786
Strong and fine, Lady Blackwood.

44:24.871 --> 44:28.206
Sister Spellman,
Lady Blackwood's bleeding too much.

44:28.291 --> 44:29.708
We'll fix her right up.

44:30.293 --> 44:33.128
My babies... Sister Zelda, my babies.

44:33.628 --> 44:35.590
They must be preserved...

44:37.382 --> 44:38.800
...at all costs.

44:50.980 --> 44:52.356
Hilda, there you are.

44:52.440 --> 44:53.690
Dr. Cee?

44:54.650 --> 44:55.818
What are you doing?

44:55.902 --> 44:58.445
You should be downstairs.
I got so worried.

44:58.528 --> 45:02.282
I'm saying a little prayer
against the tornado.

45:02.365 --> 45:03.951
Do you need me to stay?

45:05.661 --> 45:09.081
Just hold my hands. Just for a minute.

45:10.916 --> 45:12.043
Will that help?

45:12.835 --> 45:14.128
It can't hurt, can it?

45:24.012 --> 45:27.141
Susie, what happened? What did you do?

45:27.224 --> 45:31.603
I have no clue.
Maybe she just got tired and went home?

45:32.188 --> 45:33.438
No, children.

45:34.315 --> 45:35.398
She left.

45:36.108 --> 45:37.568
She left...

45:38.902 --> 45:41.822
because it's his turn now.

45:41.905 --> 45:44.574
The Crimson Rider.

45:45.284 --> 45:47.452
The Angel of Death.

45:49.121 --> 45:50.539
Can't you hear him?

45:53.668 --> 45:55.335
That horse of his?

46:09.809 --> 46:12.728
- What the hell is that now?
- That, mortal, is the main event.

46:13.186 --> 46:14.563
The Doom of Greendale.

46:17.733 --> 46:19.612
You're not your father's
firstborn son, are you?

46:20.318 --> 46:21.945
No, that would have been Tommy.

46:22.445 --> 46:23.655
What about your father?

46:24.739 --> 46:26.951
He's the firstborn son, yeah.

46:35.543 --> 46:37.420
How do I do it, Ms. Wardwell?

46:38.295 --> 46:39.297
Dig deep.

46:39.380 --> 46:41.465
It isn't just power, Sabrina.

46:42.550 --> 46:43.842
It's rage.

46:44.927 --> 46:47.429
It's the desire to change the world...

46:48.264 --> 46:49.681
and the will to do it.

46:50.349 --> 46:52.559
Command the Greendale Thirteen.

46:58.356 --> 47:01.818
I order the Greendale Thirteen to stop!

47:04.112 --> 47:07.199
Go in peace, or face my wrath!

47:18.251 --> 47:20.463
Is that it? Has the storm passed?

47:23.090 --> 47:25.342
No, it just got here.

47:26.260 --> 47:30.431
Tell me. You're not the firstborn
in your family, are you?

47:30.972 --> 47:32.557
Oldest of three boys.

47:34.768 --> 47:37.563
Hear me, hear me. Run away.
Live to see another day.

47:38.188 --> 47:41.192
Run! Go! I will be right behind you.

47:49.240 --> 47:52.077
<i>Qui affecto protego,</i>

47:52.161 --> 47:55.039
<i>mixtisque iubas serpentibus.</i>

47:57.833 --> 48:01.753
<i>Qui affecto protego,
mixtisque iubas serpentibus</i>

48:01.836 --> 48:04.340
<i>et posteris meis stirpiqu.</i>

48:05.465 --> 48:07.092
<i>Qui affecto protego.</i>

48:11.054 --> 48:13.099
Who are you to order us?

48:13.306 --> 48:16.268
We felt the wrath of Greendale once,
child.

48:16.643 --> 48:19.480
- We won't be hung again.
- No, not hung.

48:20.563 --> 48:21.731
Burned.

48:22.108 --> 48:23.900
Burn us, half-witch?

48:24.610 --> 48:26.237
We are not of this Earth.

48:26.320 --> 48:28.697
No earthly fire can burn us.

48:28.780 --> 48:30.699
No, not earthly fire.

48:31.742 --> 48:32.576
Hellfire.

48:32.659 --> 48:37.623
None but the most powerful
can summon it: Devils.

48:37.831 --> 48:40.501
And in the history of witches,
only three...

48:40.583 --> 48:42.585
Well, it's about to be four.

48:42.961 --> 48:47.842
I, Sabrina Spellman,
daughter of Edward Spellman,

48:47.925 --> 48:53.472
Child of Night, call forth...
Fire from the Pit.

48:56.141 --> 48:59.103
<i>Ater ignus, fusce fume.</i>

48:59.561 --> 49:04.817
<i>Te evoco ut potentium tuam monstres.</i>

49:04.900 --> 49:08.070
<i>Cupidibus flammis hic veni.</i>

49:08.695 --> 49:12.615
<i>Caelo sub isto, harc arborem consumo.</i>

49:13.032 --> 49:16.579
<i>Lucem tenebrasque tuas monstra.</i>

49:16.911 --> 49:21.041
<i>Impetuum tuum evoco ad devorandum.</i>

49:21.416 --> 49:25.420
<i>Hanc arborem ac omnes hospitas devora.</i>

49:44.981 --> 49:47.610
<i>And then they went up in hell flame.</i>

49:47.693 --> 49:51.030
<i>A gorgeous, searing inferno...</i>

49:51.489 --> 49:53.449
<i>consumed their souls.</i>

49:55.326 --> 49:57.327
Releasing their anger...

49:59.121 --> 50:01.623
until their charred bodies

50:01.706 --> 50:04.168
<i>fell from the sky...</i>

50:05.543 --> 50:07.003
<i>like ash.</i>

50:17.889 --> 50:19.289
<i>And once the witches</i>

50:19.349 --> 50:21.309
<i>who summoned
the Red Death were gone,</i>

50:21.393 --> 50:24.605
<i>and the wrath
that fueled him dissipated,</i>

50:25.146 --> 50:26.481
<i>the Angel, too...</i>

50:27.650 --> 50:29.275
<i>simply vanished</i>

50:29.360 --> 50:31.152
<i>as though he was never there.</i>

50:32.028 --> 50:36.407
<i>And just like that,
the witching hour was over.</i>

50:36.784 --> 50:39.536
And most everyone had survived the storm,

50:39.954 --> 50:45.668
little knowing how close
to annihilation they'd come.

50:59.681 --> 51:00.849
What happened tonight?

51:01.224 --> 51:03.978
I'm pretty sure your girlfriend just saved
the entire town.

51:05.563 --> 51:06.813
She's not my girlfriend.

51:08.106 --> 51:09.106
Not anymore.

51:11.110 --> 51:12.610
Why did you show up here?

51:12.695 --> 51:14.487
She asked me, so I came.

51:16.447 --> 51:17.447
No, but...

51:18.324 --> 51:19.324
why?

51:20.702 --> 51:21.702
Are you...

51:22.413 --> 51:25.081
- Are you, guys...
- She loves you, mortal.

51:28.168 --> 51:29.335
She'd die for you.

51:30.461 --> 51:32.047
Maybe that's worth forgiving her.

51:41.306 --> 51:44.351
Faustus, I'm sorry, but you were right.

51:44.434 --> 51:47.730
Lady Blackwood was too weak
to bring your baby into the world.

51:47.813 --> 51:50.858
Baby? I thought you said twins.

51:53.402 --> 51:57.572
Something strange
but not unheard of happened.

51:58.657 --> 52:02.369
One of your sons, the dominant one...

52:03.621 --> 52:04.996
consumed the other,

52:05.079 --> 52:07.791
the submissive one, in the womb.

52:10.168 --> 52:12.003
There is only one son...

52:12.670 --> 52:15.048
fortified by the brother he consumed.

52:18.510 --> 52:19.637
As it should be.

52:21.221 --> 52:22.472
Let me hold him.

52:33.733 --> 52:35.610
My only begotten son...

52:40.740 --> 52:41.824
and heir!

53:44.262 --> 53:47.974
I don't know what you said in that prayer
tonight, but it certainly worked.

53:49.268 --> 53:50.728
All the clouds are cleared.

53:51.353 --> 53:53.771
It's going to be a beautiful day,
Hilda Spellman.

54:05.117 --> 54:06.117
Goodnight.

54:32.351 --> 54:35.146
What happened to you earlier?

54:36.731 --> 54:40.402
Doesn't matter.
All's well that ends well, I suppose.

54:40.485 --> 54:41.320
Hilda...

54:41.402 --> 54:42.402
Yes?

54:42.570 --> 54:45.490
I've done something rather impulsive.

54:54.208 --> 54:55.375
Did you make a magic baby?

54:55.458 --> 54:56.626
It's Lady Blackwood's.

54:56.918 --> 54:57.753
Hm?

54:57.835 --> 55:02.173
A girl. I lied to Father Blackwood.
I said he only had one child.

55:02.632 --> 55:03.632
Why?

55:04.259 --> 55:06.302
To protect the babe, Hilda.

55:07.471 --> 55:10.056
She's a girl, born before her brother.

55:10.932 --> 55:14.228
And the High Priest,
I feared what he would've done to her.

55:14.811 --> 55:17.481
But we can raise her.
We've done it before.

55:17.940 --> 55:21.652
We'll keep it a secret, you and I.
Together, as sisters.

55:21.735 --> 55:22.735
Forever and ever!

55:22.820 --> 55:24.070
I'm moving out.

55:24.195 --> 55:25.195
What?

55:25.697 --> 55:29.284
I'm moving out... of this bedroom.

55:29.659 --> 55:32.954
I think it's time I had a room of my own.

55:45.425 --> 55:47.510
The Church of Night is ours, boys.

55:48.512 --> 55:50.389
This is the Dark Lord's sign.

55:51.472 --> 55:52.516
His blessing...

55:53.307 --> 55:55.018
that we are in the right.

55:56.603 --> 56:00.023
Hail to my firstborn son.

56:00.815 --> 56:02.025
Hail Judas!

56:02.150 --> 56:04.570
Hail Judas! Hail Satan!

56:04.652 --> 56:06.989
Hail Judas! Hail Satan!

56:07.072 --> 56:09.365
Hail Judas! Hail Satan!

56:09.449 --> 56:10.449
Hail Judas!

56:25.423 --> 56:27.634
You... changed your hair.

56:28.510 --> 56:29.594
Yeah.

56:30.721 --> 56:32.222
Thanks for sending that guy, Nick.

56:33.472 --> 56:34.472
He...

56:36.143 --> 56:37.853
He said you saved the whole town tonight.

56:39.146 --> 56:41.648
Well, it was a group effort.

56:44.650 --> 56:46.235
I wanted to check on you.

56:47.403 --> 56:50.282
And apologize again, Harvey.

56:51.365 --> 56:53.994
For all the secrets, for Tommy.

56:55.077 --> 56:56.079
For everything.

56:57.789 --> 57:00.208
I truly am sorry.

57:00.291 --> 57:01.293
I know.

57:03.795 --> 57:04.838
I know you are.

57:05.338 --> 57:06.882
So, what if you we start over?

57:09.259 --> 57:10.802
No more secrets this time. We just...

57:10.885 --> 57:11.885
I don't...

57:13.931 --> 57:15.806
I don't think that's such a good idea.

57:17.726 --> 57:19.186
I don't know if it's safe...

57:20.144 --> 57:21.480
for me to be around you.

57:22.313 --> 57:23.313
Or Roz...

57:24.231 --> 57:25.317
or Susie.

57:25.400 --> 57:26.400
Why not?

57:27.152 --> 57:29.028
I had to do something tonight...

57:31.197 --> 57:32.324
that scares me.

57:33.032 --> 57:34.032
Harvey...

57:36.619 --> 57:38.163
it touched something...

57:39.748 --> 57:42.166
dark inside me.

57:44.878 --> 57:48.465
I love you too much to risk
anything bad happening to you.

57:57.431 --> 57:58.431
Can I...

58:00.559 --> 58:02.144
Can I get one last kiss?

58:23.166 --> 58:25.085
<i>And that, as they say...</i>

58:25.835 --> 58:26.835
<i>was that.</i>

58:27.253 --> 58:29.505
All things according to his plan.

58:30.548 --> 58:33.385
Though I never really get
the credit I deserve.

58:34.719 --> 58:37.139
The best and worst things...

58:38.139 --> 58:39.391
happen in the shadows.

58:40.809 --> 58:45.438
Well, this is all a very long-winded way
of my telling you that...

58:47.190 --> 58:50.027
I'm an amazing teacher,
Principal Hawthorne.

58:51.445 --> 58:55.865
No one but me could've gotten Sabrina
so far along the Path of Night.

58:57.534 --> 58:59.452
Who the hell are you, lady?

59:02.039 --> 59:03.039
Who am I?

59:06.208 --> 59:08.085
Well, I'm not Mary Wardwell...

59:08.795 --> 59:10.505
though I do enjoy her body.

59:12.840 --> 59:16.719
I'm the Mother of Demons,
the Dawn of Doom,

59:17.471 --> 59:19.139
Satan's concubine.

59:20.639 --> 59:22.349
I'm Lilith, dear boy.

59:23.268 --> 59:24.686
First wife to Adam,

59:24.811 --> 59:27.898
saved from despair by a fallen angel.

59:28.731 --> 59:33.277
I call myself Madame Satan in his honor.

59:35.072 --> 59:36.155
But soon...

59:37.907 --> 59:38.907
very soon...

59:40.869 --> 59:42.536
I'll have a new title.

59:43.246 --> 59:44.246
You see...

59:47.125 --> 59:51.797
once I finish grooming Sabrina
to take my place as Satan's foot-soldier,

59:54.132 --> 59:58.094
I'll earn a crown
and a throne by his side.

01:00:02.641 --> 01:00:03.974
Who am I?

01:00:15.277 --> 01:00:17.655
I'm the future Queen of Hell.

01:00:26.039 --> 01:00:27.958
I did so leave you leftovers.

01:00:29.960 --> 01:00:32.086
Oh, stop squawking, and just say it.

01:00:32.753 --> 01:00:33.963
Forgive me, madame,

01:00:34.047 --> 01:00:36.173
but doesn't it seem
that Satan is grooming Sabrina

01:00:36.257 --> 01:00:38.467
to reign at his side, not you?

01:00:40.052 --> 01:00:44.974
But the Dark Lord wouldn't betray
my eternal service like that, Stolas.

01:00:46.726 --> 01:00:48.061
Even if he would,

01:00:49.103 --> 01:00:53.023
there would be a very simple way
to deal with Sabrina.

01:01:08.539 --> 01:01:10.876
She's still Sabrina, Harvey.

01:01:11.208 --> 01:01:12.835
She's still the girl we know.

01:01:13.043 --> 01:01:14.461
I don't know, Susie.

01:01:14.545 --> 01:01:16.005
Something had changed,

01:01:16.547 --> 01:01:17.715
and not just her hair.

01:01:18.800 --> 01:01:21.927
But she's still coming to school, right?

01:01:24.014 --> 01:01:25.849
I mean, we're still her friends?

